  "text": "For experiments with only two sequenced populations or time points (e.g. \"input\" and \"selected\"), Enrich2 calculates the slope between the two time point log ratios, which is equivalent to frequently used ratio-based scoring methods [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Unlike previous implementations of ratio-based scoring, we provide standard error estimates for each score using Poisson assumptions (see \"Methods\").",
